Description: 
	A simple client-server connection over local same machine IP: 127.0.01
	Port: 8080 and using TCP protocol

How to run:
	1. On terminal, change directory into 'HW2' folder
	2. Open up a second terminal window
	3. type 'make' to compile both files, client.c and server.c
	4. On one window run server as './server', Do this first
	5. On other window run client as './client', Do this second
	6. Type into client window and press enter
	7. message should appear on server window. 
	8. 'Ctrl+C' to end demo

